{
  "texts": [
    "Accordingly, the overlaps between Variant-2 and Variant-4 are 14% and 61%, respectively.",
    "Variant-3 and Variant-4 overlap in 23% and 29% of the cases, respectively.",
    "What already becomes obvious at this stage of our comparison is that Variant-0 is highly selective.",
    "The other insight is that the list from Variant-4 is clearly distinct from the lists of the other variants.",
    "We expect that these similarities and differences also have an influence on the characteristics of the HCRs in the different lists."
  ]
}